  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is done to estimate prevalence of the main detectable lung and cardiovascular
      complications by an ultrasound realized in room of post-interventional supervision at the
      patients whose duration of general anesthesia is superior at one hour after a surgery to risk
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
